 by users, it can help improve the performance of the site.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When WP-Optimize caching is launched, it will have many features including minimal configuration, cache pre-loading and page caching. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We will be releasing an updated blog with further details once the feature is close to release, so be sure to keep an eye out for further details!</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The caching feature will be the latest in a series of site optimization options that aim to make WP-Optimize your one stop shop for improving your sites speed and performance. Along with image optimization and lazy loading, the addition of caching aims to make WP-Optimize the only WordPress optimization tool you need.</span></p>\n<p><span>To find out more about all the additional features of WP-Optimize, visit the </span><a href="https://getwpo.com/"><span>website</span></a><span> today.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-give-sneak-peek-of-upcoming-caching-feature/">WP-Optimize give sneak-peek of upcoming caching feature</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:85:"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-give-sneak-peek-of-upcoming-caching-feature/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1